            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏好 恒指升17點報25945點 量化派高開1.65倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股連續3日反彈後，今早開市初段仍偏好。恒生指數開市報25945點，升17點或0.047%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5613點，則跌5點或0.1%；國企指數以9156點開市，亦跌5點或0.06%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股個別發展，阿里巴巴(09988)開報154元，跌0.52%；騰訊(00700)開報618元，跌0.24%；美團(03690)開報103.6元，跌0.19%；京東(09618)開報114.7元，跌0.09%；小米(01810)開報40.24元，升0.35%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於兩大藍籌國際金融股，滙控(00005)開報109元，升1.3%；友邦(01299)開報81.1元，升0.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015)昨收市後公布業績，上季由盈轉虧；該股今早開報71.65元，微跌0.07%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羊小咩母公司量化派(02685)今早登場，以26元開市，較招股價9.8元高1.65倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15460551-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8717%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125945%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8f%e5%8c%96%e6%b4%be%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b1-65",
